lan\nThe execution plan decision log (TASK-im.md) says: "使用数据库自增 bigseria
l" for `sequence_id`. But the implementation uses `Snowflake.nextId()` (applicat
ion-layer snowflake). This is a deviation from the plan. However, the tech-debt-
