layer approach IS the planned direction.\n\nActually wait, let me re-read. The t
ech-debt-tracker says:\n> `MessageEntity.sequence_id` 使用 TypeORM `@Generated("
increment")` 与 MySQL 非主键 AUTO_INCREMENT 存在兼容性风险\n\nBut I didn\'t see 
