ce identical `sequence_id` values across instances because the implementation is
purely timestamp + sequence counter with no unique worker/node identifier. Under
high concurrency with multiple API instances, duplicate sequence_ids are possibl
e.\n\n## Minor Issues:\n\n5. **`SwChatBubble` uses `MediaQuery.of(context).size.
